# HoneLandingPages Memory

## Project Overview
WordPress landing pages theme at `themes/HoneLandingPages/`. Build with `yarn build` from the theme directory. Local dev at `http://localhost:8081`. Build output in `build/`, source in `src/`.

## Page Speed Optimization Patterns
See `page-speed.md` for detailed findings from mens-hrt-enhanced-pdp-1 optimization session.

Key tools: Chrome DevTools MCP (already in session), Lighthouse CLI via `npx lighthouse`.

## Key Files
- `src/functions.php` — HONE_PAGE_TEMPLATES array, asset enqueuing
- `src/header.php` — shared `<head>`, font preloads, GTM script
- `src/static/scss/settings/fonts.scss` — font-face declarations
- `src/static/js/pages/{slug}.bundle.js` — page-specific JS entry points
